code: @Override public void afterPropertiesSet() throws IOException {     Properties props = new Properties().     props.load(new ClassPathResource("application.properties").getInputStream()).     String value = props.getProperty("message").     if (value != null) {         this.message = value.     } }
public void run(String... args) {     System.err.println("Hello Embedded " + this.message + "!"). }
